/*===========================================================================

FUNCTION sdss_throttle_reset_cntrs

DESCRIPTION
  This function resets the throttling counters.Called when SD determines to
  idle on the acquired system.

DEPENDENCIES
  This function must be called before any other sdss_xxx is called.

RETURN VALUE

SIDE EFFECTS
  None.

===========================================================================*/
